title: Symmetrical language/environment in SET handlers
summary: Fixed dead code warnings by implementing language/environment suffix building in SET operations to match GET behavior. Added build_storage_key() helper function.

title: Process log format migration to YYMMDD-PXX
summary: Migrated process log format from P001 to date-based YYMMDD-PXX format. Removed redundant date column from INDEX.csv. Updated all documentation and examples.
